Swarm Catching
<h2>Catching Swarms</h2>

<p>Swarms are great fun! They give us a chance to show off, share our passion about bees and how important they are to our lives.</p>
<p>They also provide use with new bees for our operations. You will soon see that there is prose and cons to keeping them.
